        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         If you write a newsletter that covers tech and finance, you kinda have to write about Gamestop / WSB / Robinhood. That means that plenty of really smart people have written great analyses. See:
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE2OwyAMhU9Tdo2AhCZdsOhmrhHxY1JUAgicyeT2wySLsSwb2TJP7zMKYUnlkDlVJH9lxiODjLDXAIhQyFahzN5K9uBTL4YnsXKwbBIT8XV2BWBVPkgsG5C86eCNQp_ieUEpF-QtqRse0-iMdUpT9nyKkVPXu8E5IbR56EtXbdZDNCDhG8qRIpAg34i53vrXjX-13Pe9M8lHC_XTHmsbLWqFiinfC6hwX1X5ALYWfd6CwlQq8ZJTziinjPWiRce6VeefDGXIvbkNdF14VzddUZnzV1JkTKhT8XFp68-7SYRz0ezNra9b9HjMEJUOYC_neAE8WcwLRCgNrJ0VNmyMs2kcheBCXE4bmp7TqR_pQJqyTe0q_ov-AqvGi5o" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Jill Carlson
         </a>
         ,
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkc9uwyAMxp-m3BLxJzTZgcMue40IgpugJRiBs65vP7c9DCFs_Mn-0I_FE6xYH65gI_E8ZnoUcBnubQciqOJsUOcUnbrqydjhQ0Q3RDXZSaQ23yrA4dPuqJ4gyhn2tHhKmF8dUmorNuejhsn4SYIZvYWgzHUBOxrpg5yMub19_RkT5AUc_EB9YAaxu42otIv5vOgv3vf7vQ874hGgrv2CB9ewpMx2nPlKadmhcaqlVp1Unf7gS4UYE3VUfYTaOsxdxZDyhhg7X-FZCEhb11IElm_d6g9ohEUk9xwktVTKWF696o9QfgvUoZjlMshj1X07QyO_fD_fI6rLSAFryivL3xtP2l8Ck5k5HmdO9Jgh-7BDfEOjN_sXxnmFDJX_JM6emLjSahpHa7W1b0hM1WiGNspBsHNE7sr_pn-V-55Y" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Matt Levine
         </a>
         , and
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVUEluwzAMfE10NLTG9kGHXvoNQQtjC7ElQaKb-vdV40NRggtAghzOeIuw5HrqkhuS32TwLKATvNoGiFDJ0aCaGDS780koOZOgZWCTmkhs5lEBdhs3jfUAUg63RW8x5vTeoJQrsmo73e388MqL-zyPltFxnIX0bh4le4CjF649QoTkQcMX1DMnIJteEUu7iY8b_-webPJ5aIdraP1z8HnvzdKjvtaIsOb-qgNsJGpOOaOcMiZUt4ENuyvfBaoswt8k3Rf-7w6pOmV0uca09PFztTts70GnZHrdjxTxNJCs2yBcbPES7c3fLJCgdjGDsdilYpxN46gUV-pi1-UQnE5ipJJ05JD7VvoD_QH074YF" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Alex Danco
         </a>
         for some thorough and thoughtful takes.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         But I haven\xe2\x80\x99t yet seen the take that I want to read: that this was inevitable. Given how Robinhood built and incentivized itself, it would have taken a black swan event for the company
         <em>
          not
         </em>
         to end up in this situation at some point. And it\xe2\x80\x99s only going to get crazier.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Let me get this out of the way upfront: I am clearly conflicted here, on both sides.
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUEtuxSAMPM1jGfFt0gWLbnoNxMdJ0EsAgdM2ty8vkVrLsmVb49GMtwhLrqcuuSF5FYNnAZ3gu22ACJUcDaqJQbM3Pgkl30nQMrBJTSQ2M1eA3cZNYz2AlMNt0VuMOV0ISrkiq2aKKsGYm8PcV0zO0ol5BKqCHUfq6c1rjxAhedDwBfXMCcimV8TSHuLjwT973u8Hn_c-pIwu15gWEjWnnFFOGROqx8CG3ZWfAlUW4R-S7gsf2uEaWv98oUnVf-h-fq52h-06dAbT-36kiKeBZN0G4daGt0WXWrNAgtqtC8ZiN4ZxNo2jUlypW0sXLzidxEgl6cwhd1T6J_0FJSx_Ig" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Public
         </a>
         has sponsored Not Boring, the Not Boring Syndicate invested in
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM1uwyAQhJ8mHC1-TOwcOPTS10Bg1g6qDQjWcf323cSHrtAu0mg0-mZyCEuupym5IXsvi2cBk-BoKyBCZXuDamMw4i5HpfsHC6YPYtQji83OFWBzcTVYd2Bl92ucHMacPg7OpWZPI7wH78IsgphBhFk_hkHpEPp7UO4B85Xr9hAhTWDgBfXMCdhqnoil3dTXTX7TO46ji-kFDae8kQdqRx8SWDSSS8ElF0Jpmk50my-_BWpf1HTr-bbIru2-oZt-3iZWTcroc41pIfnn6TZYPwIxWLrbniKeFpLzK4QLD6-WPsB2gQSV2gvWIXUjpBiHQWup9YVD_EryUQ28Z5QcMrnSf-gfW--B1g" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Composer
         </a>
         , I know people who I like and respect who have invested in Robinhood, and I trade some of my money in Robinhood.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         None of those facts change the way that I think about this situation. I have the paper trail to prove it. I\xe2\x80\x99ve been
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMtuxCAMRb8mLEc8h2TBolI1u35DxMPNoEkAgdNp_r7MZFFkgS3r-uLjLcKS62FKbkhe14xHAZPg2VZAhEr2BnWOwbArH4WSEwlGBjaqkcQ2f1eAzcbVYN2BlN2t0VuMOb0VlHJF7sa6AIoqzZi2bnQT5WKyfrp6brUPTp6-dg8RkgcDP1CPnICs5o5Y2iA-Bn7rgc_4-tHF561XxfrH8dWThhb31pNJMqoUGwXT-sq0pOMgbl3-ySmJhlPOKKeMCdXPhV02V34LVFmEHyTdFn5pu-vD_OPlQKpJGV2uMS29_bjbDdZ3o28593fbU8RjhmTdCuEEgCfHN5J5gQS18w2zxU6PcTZqrRRX6ly4ExKcjkJTSbpzyF2V_k3_AFNxiIY" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          expecting this for years
