        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         The Robinhood story is a story about risk and chaos. If you introduce more chaos into the system than you\xe2\x80\x99re ready to handle, the chaos is gonna getcha.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
